OL,3,CRhun ap Iorwerth and his top team have
OL,4,Cto make an immediate mark
OL,6,FNot since the first Welsh Government
OL,7,F(or Executive as it was then called)
OL,8,Fback in 1999 has there been such an
OL,9,Fentirely new set of ministers running
OL,10,Fthe show, but then, this is the first
OL,11,Ftime since then that a new party has
OL,12,Fbeen in charge.
OL,14,FBut while Rhun ap Iorwerth's first
OL,15,Fcabinet may lack government
OL,16,Fexperience, the ministers within it
OL,17,Fbring many years' experience elsewhere.
OL,19,FOnly Elin Jones, the former Llywydd or
OL,20,FPresiding Officer has been a
OL,21,Fgovernment minister before.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/7
