OL,3,CRhun ap Iorwerth and his top team have
OL,4,Cto make an immediate mark
OL,6,FShe was the Rural Affairs minister
OL,7,Ffrom 2007 when Plaid Cymru formed a
OL,8,Fcoalition government with Labour.
OL,10,FShe now has the crucial role of
OL,11,FFinance Minister, the equivalent of
OL,12,FChancellor of The Exchequer.
OL,14,FAs well as balancing the books, she'll
OL,15,Fbe the Welsh Government's chief
OL,16,Fnegotiator with the UK Government,
OL,17,Fpushing for change to what Plaid Cymru
OL,18,Fargues is an unfair funding settlement.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/7
