OL,3,CRhun ap Iorwerth and his top team have
OL,4,Cto make an immediate mark
OL,6,FThe party's manifesto promised the
OL,7,Fappointment of a minister for public
OL,8,Fhealth, and that has been fulfilled.
OL,10,FThe role goes to Assembly Member,
OL,11,FNerys Evans who authored a report in
OL,12,F2023 into allegations of bullying and
OL,13,Fmisogyny within the party.
OL,15,FFrom Plaid Cymru's lowest point to its
OL,16,Fhighest.
OL,26,@rD@Fsw
