OL,3,CRhun ap Iorwerth and his top team have
OL,4,Cto make an immediate mark
OL,6,FThe leader at that time, Adam Price,
OL,7,Fwho was forced to step down following
OL,8,Fthe report becomes Minister for
OL,9,FEnterprise, Connectivity and Energy,
OL,10,Fplaying into his experience in
OL,11,Fbusiness and the study of business.
OL,13,FOther appointments are all senior
OL,14,Ffigures within Plaid Cymru who have a
OL,15,Fwealth of experience inside and
OL,16,Foutside the party, even if they're new
OL,17,FSenedd Members.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/7
