OL,3,CRhun ap Iorwerth and his top team have
OL,4,Cto make an immediate mark
OL,6,FOne who isn't a member is the former
OL,7,FMP Elfyn Llwyd, a practising lawyer,
OL,8,Fwho is being put forward as Counsel
OL,9,FGeneral, the Welsh Government's legal
OL,10,Fchief and a post which doesn't have to
OL,11,Fbe filled by an elected politician.
OL,13,FThe new First Minister is likely to
OL,14,Fturn to him for wise counsel on a
OL,15,Frange of issues, not just legal
OL,16,Fmatters.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/7
