OL,3,CRhun ap Iorwerth and his top team have
OL,4,Cto make an immediate mark
OL,6,FRhun ap Iorwerth could have appointed
OL,7,Fup to 17 ministers, but has appointed
OL,8,F13, leaving plenty of other MSs to
OL,9,Fpopulate committees and act as
OL,10,Fbackbenchers.
OL,12,FNo previous Welsh Government has had
OL,13,Fso many non-government members, which
OL,14,Fcould prove to be a blessing or a
OL,15,Fcurse if frustrations emerge as the
OL,16,Fcompromises of government.
OL,18,FWhat issue might provoke the first
OL,19,Frebellion for a Plaid Cymru government?
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/7
